plot: As Luke's life hangs in the balance, repercussions from the devastating event are the catalyst for some life-changing decisions for those around him.

With Luke lying between life and death, Batwoman attempts to bring the man who shot him to justice and clear his name, while Sophie confronts Jacob and tries to get him to do the right thing. Alice tries to find the codeword that will restore Kate's memories, and has a meeting with Ocean.—Gislef
